 \U0001f552 Employment Type: Full-Time
 \U0001f4bc Level: Entry-Level / Junior
We are looking for a motivated Junior Developer / DevOps Engineer to join our tech team. In this role, you will assist in building, deploying, and maintaining applications while supporting infrastructure and automation processes. This is an excellent opportunity for early-career professionals to gain hands-on experience with DevOps practices and full lifecycle development.
\U0001f3af Key Responsibilities
