Maintain infrastructure as code and configuration management tools.
Participate in code reviews and documentation of processes.
Stay updated with DevOps best practices, tools, and emerging technologies.
\u2705 Requirements
Basic proficiency in programming languages such as Python, Java, or JavaScript.
Familiarity with Linux/Unix systems, version control (Git), and basic networking concepts.
