Eagerness to learn and collaborate in a team-oriented environment.
Previous internships, projects, or personal experience in development or DevOps is a plus.
\U0001f31f What We Offer
Hands-on experience with full-stack development and DevOps practices.
Mentorship and guidance from experienced engineers.
